The Mage Guard are a small but well-trained force of growing number within the Kingdom of Kohlingen. The symbol of Mystra emblazoned on their cloaks, they work diligently alongside the Silver Dragons under the command of the Magister.
Set into a copper band is a single green eye, constantly scanning the area and blinking now and then.  When the eye spots something, a faint tingle can be felt in the ring finger.
